# --- THE FAILURE TEST.  Trigonal pencil = the u-map (u has 3 poles).
# Lemma A predicts: for W = (2 of 3 preimages) over each point of a u-fiber
# E0(c), the Petri kernel on the s-slice = h^0(omega_C - E0(c)) = h^0(N) = 2,
